PAYMENT RECEIVED
================

Dear <%= @client.name %>,

Thank you! Your payment has been received.

We have received your payment for Invoice <%= @invoice.invoice_number %>.

PAYMENT DETAILS
---------------
Invoice Number: <%= @invoice.invoice_number %>
<% if @invoice.paid_at %>
Payment Date: <%= @invoice.paid_at.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %>
<% end %>
<% if @invoice.payment_method.present? %>
Payment Method: <%= @invoice.payment_method.titleize %>
<% end %>
Amount Paid: <%= number_to_currency(@invoice.total_amount) %>

